title: Jet Cash
author: Jet Cash
content: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PdKRx30s6skThis year's cheese rolling contest put a bit of a strain on the emergency services. It's one of England's quaint old traditions. Heve you got anything like that in your country?

comments.author: Cointxz
comments.body: Quote from: Jet Cash on June 04, 2023, 01:09:05 PMhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PdKRx30s6skThis year's cheese rolling contest put a bit of a strain on the emergency services. It's one of England's quaint old traditions. Heve you got anything like that in your country?I watch a lot of this video on facebook shared by many friends in the past. I don’t understand why participants is very eager to get that cheese in exchange for the pain in their body? Is there other prize aside from cheese that makes the participants motivated?The closest event that we have on our country is agawan buko(https://youtu.be/zJDUMr9nSG4]. It’s like American Football but there’s no rules on how you will get the buko(coconut) to other player. Also players whole body is cover with oil to make it slippery and very hard to catch. This is the game that I know with same unique objectives and rules.

comments.author: DeathAngel
comments.body: I think that must go down as extreme sport, seriously after watching the video haha. It seems so dangerous but hey who am I to judge.Imagine the lactic acid & thigh burn running up that hill. If they have fun & don’t get a serious injury then good luck to them.
